          <div class="content-items">
            <h3>Indications Search</h3>
            <p>A drug indication describes the approved conditions, diseases, or states for which a drug can
              safely and effectively be used. These indications may vary between regions, health systems,
              and countries depending on how they are defined, the products that are being used, and the
              regulatory body that is approving them.</p>
            <p>Drug indications can be searched and filtered via the DrugBank API in several ways. Use the
              form below to see examples of how this may be done.</p>
            <div class="example-box container-fluid" id="step-1">
              <div class="row">
                <div class="example-col col-sm-4">
                  <div id="loader"><img src="images/pill.gif" alt="Pill"></div>
                  <form id="indication_search_form" action="#" accept-charset="UTF-8" method="post">
                    <input name="utf8" type="hidden" value="âœ“"><input type="hidden" name="authenticity_token"
                      value="xB03o12Uuz3qyNNFaBWdUQYftJQsOAs4jxNZ7HTOT/1as11kUp9ukBzkMhFWRiPIIeFR16gPQOIXZ+8gZAvMBA==">
                    <div class="form-group">
                      <label for="indication_name">Indication Name</label>
                      <input type="text" name="indication_name" id="indication_name" class="form-control">
                      <label for="specificity">Specificity</label>
                      <select name="specificity_select" id="specificity_select" class="form-control">
                        <option value="">Name Matches Only</option>
                        <option value="specific">Include More Specific</option>
                        <option value="general">Include More General</option>
                      </select>
                      <label for="kind">Kind (select up to 3 or leave blank for all)</label>
                      <select name="kind_select[]" id="kind_select" multiple="multiple" class="form-control">
                        <option value="treatment_of">Treatment of</option>
                        <option value="prevention_of">Prevention of</option>
                        <option value="prophylaxis_of">Prophylaxis of</option>
                        <option value="symptomatic_treatment_of">Symptomatic treatment of</option>
                        <option value="management_of">Management of</option>
                        <option value="for_therapy">For therapy</option>
                        <option value="adjunct_therapy_in_prevention_of">Adjunct therapy in prevention of</option>
                        <option value="adjunct_therapy_in_treatment_of">Adjunct therapy in treatment of</option>
                        <option value="adjunct_therapy_in_management_of">Adjunct therapy in management of</option>
                        <option value="adjunct_therapy_in_prophylaxis_of">Adjunct therapy in prophylaxis of</option>
                        <option value="adjunct_for_therapy">Adjunct for therapy</option>
                        <option value="used_in_combination_to_treat">Used in combination to treat</option>
                        <option value="used_in_combination_for_therapy">Used in combination for therapy</option>
                        <option value="used_in_combination_to_induce">Used in combination to induce</option>
                        <option value="used_in_combination_to_manage">Used in combination to manage</option>
                        <option value="used_in_combination_to_prevent">Used in combination to prevent</option>
                        <option value="used_in_combination_for_prophylaxis_of">Used in combination for prophylaxis of</option>
                        <option value="used_in_combination_for_symptomatic_treatment_of">Used in combination for symptomatic treatment of</option>
                        <option value="used_in_combination_as_diagnostic_agent">Used in combination as diagnostic agent</option>
                        <option value="used_in_combination_for_diagnostic_process">Used in combination for diagnostic process</option>
                        <option value="used_in_combination_to_reverse">Used in combination to reverse</option>
                        <option value="induction_of">Induction of</option>
                        <option value="reversal_of">Reversal of</option>
                        <option value="diagnostic_agent">Diagnostic agent</option>
                        <option value="used_as_adjunct_in_combination_to_manage">Used as adjunct in combination to manage</option>
                        <option value="used_as_adjunct_in_combination_to_prevent">Used as adjunct in combination to prevent</option>
                        <option value="used_as_adjunct_in_combination_to_treat">Used as adjunct in combination to treat</option>
                      </select>
                      <label for="off_label">Off Label</label>
                      <select name="off_label_select" id="off_label_select" class="form-control">
                        <option value="">Include Off Label</option>
                        <option value="false">Exclude Off Label</option>
                        <option value="true">Off Label Only</option>
                      </select>
                      <label for="otc_use">OTC Use</label>
                      <select name="otc_use_select" id="otc_use_select" class="form-control">
                        <option value="">Include OTC</option>
                        <option value="false">Exclude OTC</option>
                        <option value="true">OTC Only</option>
                      </select>
                    </div>
                    <div class="actions"><input type="submit" name="commit" value="Search" id="indication_search"
                      class="btn db-primary" data-url="https://dev.drugbankplus.com/guides/tutorials/api_request"
                      data-disable-with="Search">
                    </div>
                  </form>
                </div>
                <div class="code-col col-sm-8">
                  <ul class="nav nav-pills" role="tablist">
